    </head>
    <body id="page-top">
        <!-- Navigation-->
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light fixed-top" id="mainNav">
            <div class="container">
                <a class="navbar-brand js-scroll-trigger" href="#page-top">Pyr'Teck</a><button class="navbar-toggler navbar-toggler-right" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarResponsive" aria-controls="navbarResponsive" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">Menu<i class="fas fa-bars"></i></button>
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarResponsive">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
                        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link js-scroll-trigger" href="#mostabout">Présentation</a></li>
                        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link js-scroll-trigger" href="#projects">Projets</a></li>
                        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link js-scroll-trigger" href="#signup">Contact</a></li>
                        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link js-scroll-trigger" href="../Public/index.php?route=blog">MyBlog</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
        <!-- Masthead-->
        <header class="masthead">
            <div class="container d-flex h-100 align-items-center">
                <div class="mx-auto text-center">
                    <h1 class="mx-auto my-0 text-uppercase">Le développement au coeur des Pyrénées</h1>
                    <h2 class="text-white-50 mx-auto mt-2 mb-5">Vous cherchez un développeur ayant la connaissance de Symfony</h2>
                    <a class="btn btn-primary js-scroll-trigger" href="#about">Qui suis-je?</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>
        <!-- About-->
        <section class="about-section text-center" id="about">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                        <h2 class="text-white mb-4">Etudiant en développement web Symfony chez OC</h2>
                        <p class="text-white-50">Une reconversion incontournable pour moi, cette formation va me permettre de poser un cadre sur ce qui était un hobbie ++</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <img class="img-fluid" src="Images/ipad.png" alt="" />
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- Almost on me-->
        <section class="projects-section bg-light" id="mostabout">
            <div class="container">
                <!-- Featured Project Row-->
                <div class="row align-items-center no-gutters mb-4 mb-lg-5">
                    <div class="col-xl-8 col-lg-7"><img class="img-fluid mb-3 mb-lg-0" src="Images/bg-masthead.jpg" alt="" /></div>
                    <div class="col-xl-4 col-lg-5">
                        <div class="featured-text text-center text-lg-left">
                            <h4>Un peu plus sur moi.</h4>
                            <p class="text-black-50 mb-0">De cursus technique, et après avoir passé plusieurs années sur la réalité du terrain, je me suis spécialisé dans le domaine de l'informatique, en commençant comme support métier sur nos outils manufacturing, puis un peu de développement .... les prémisses d'une grande passion!!</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="projects-section bg-light" id="projects">
                <!-- Project One Row-->
                {% for post in posts %}
                    {% if post.id is even %}
                        {% set placeImg = 'text-lg-left'%}
                    {% else %}
                        {% set placeImg = 'text-lg-right'%}
                    {% endif %}
                    <div class="row justify-content-center no-gutters mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                        <div class="col-lg-6"><img class="img-fluid" src="Images/ChaletHydro.jpg" alt="" /></div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="bg-black text-center h-100 project">
                                <div class="d-flex h-100">
                                    <div class="project-text w-100 my-auto text-center {{placeImg}}">
                                        <h4 class="text-white">{{post.title}}</h4>
                                        <p class="mb-0 text-white-50">{{post.chapo}}</p>
                                        <hr class="d-none d-lg-block mb-0 ml-0" />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- Signup-->
        <section class="signup-section" id="signup">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-10 col-lg-8 mx-auto text-center">
                        <i class="far fa-paper-plane fa-2x mb-2 text-white"></i>
                        <h2 class="text-white mb-5">Contactez-moi :</h2>
                        <div class="text-left text-white">
                            {% if message %}
                                {% if statutmessage == 2 %}
                                    <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                                {% else %}
                                    <div class="alert alert-warning alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                                {% endif %}
                                    <strong>Message :</strong> {{message}}
                                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
                                        <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                                    </button>
                                </div> 
                            {% endif %}
                            <form name="sentMessage" id="contactForm" class="was-validated" method="post" action="../public/index.php?route=sendMail" novalidate>
                                <div class="control-group">
                                    <div class="form-group floating-label-form-group controls">
                                    <label>Name</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Name" id="name" name="name" value="" required data-validation-required-message="Please enter your name.">
                                    <p class="help-block text-danger"></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="control-group">
                                    <div class="form-group floating-label-form-group controls">
                                    <label>Email Address</label>
                                    <input type="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Email Address" id="email" name="email" value="" required data-validation-required-message="Please enter your email address.">
                                    <p class="help-block text-danger"></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="control-group">
                                    <div class="form-group floating-label-form-group controls">
                                    <label>Message</label>
                                    <textarea rows="5" class="form-control" placeholder="Message" id="message" name="message" value="" required data-validation-required-message="Please enter a message."></textarea>
                                    <p class="help-block text-danger"></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <br>
                                <div id="success"></div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="sendMessageButton">Send</button>
                                </div>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- Contact-->
        <section class="contact-section bg-black">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-3 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                        <div class="card py-4 h-100">
                            <div class="card-body text-center">
                                <i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt text-primary mb-2"></i>
                                <h4 class="text-uppercase m-0">Addresse</h4>
                                <hr class="my-4" />
                                <div class="small text-black-50">Pyren FRANCE</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                        <div class="card py-4 h-100">
                            <div class="card-body text-center">
                                <i class="fas fa-envelope text-primary mb-2"></i>
                                <h4 class="text-uppercase m-0">Email</h4>
                                <hr class="my-4" />
                                <div class="small text-black-50"><a href="#!">hello@yourdomain.com</a></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                        <div class="card py-4 h-100">
                            <div class="card-body text-center">
                                <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt text-primary mb-2"></i>
                                <h4 class="text-uppercase m-0">Téléphone</h4>
                                <hr class="my-4" />
                                <div class="small text-black-50">+1 (555) 902-8832</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                        <div class="card py-4 h-100">
                            <div class="card-body text-center">
                                <i class="fas fa-id-card text-primary mb-2"></i>
                                <h4 class="text-uppercase m-0">Cursus</h4>
                                <hr class="my-4" />
                                <div class="small text-black-50"><a href="Files/CV Franck.pdf">Mon Curriculum Vitae</a></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="social d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <a class="mx-2" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/franck-dartois-5b01b2154/"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a><a class="mx-2" href="https://www.facebook.com/franck.dartois2/"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a><a class="mx-2" href="https://github.com/Franck-Dev"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- Footer-->
        <footer class="footer bg-black small text-center text-white-50"><div class="container">Copyright © Your Website 2020</div></footer>
